text: The Aérospatiale SA-360 Dauphin is a French helicopter. It is a single- turboshaft aircraft. It can hold eight passengers. Some were used by militaries, but most of them are civilian. It is the basis of the famous Aérospatiale SA-365 Dauphin 2. Category:French military aircraft Dauphin Category:Helicopters
title: Aérospatiale SA-360 Dauphin
